title: 820-4924-A .430ma no fan, no chime, no boot
message:
Hi, I have this board which I dont know what else to do to it, I get all_sys_pwrgd but get no chime, and no image on it. When I connect it to the magsafe 2 (original magsafe 2 85watts, no adapter 1->2) I get a green light, and then it turns orange, no fan or chime...
ppbus_g3h = 12.60
pp3v42_g3h= 3.42
all_sys_pwrgd= 3.3v

In adition to this, and because I got stuck diagnosing this board, can you please help me sending me a document or link to the  explanation of the power on sequence on the macbooks? I can fix back light, ISL issues and some others, but this is the 3rd month I am using the forum and I really dont think I have learned a lot from it, I really want this to work, but I need help to learn this stuff... thank you...

title: 820-4924-A .430ma no fan, no chime, no boot
message:

Did you check for USB activity?

title: 820-4924-A .430ma no fan, no chime, no boot
message:
That means the power on sequence is not completed.
Check PM_PCH_PWROK and PM_PCH_SYS_PWROK.
Akso check CPU_VCCST_PWRGD.
